{"title":"尖桩和约翰逊","authors":["袁水拍","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖桩和约翰逊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍  诗  方成  画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍竹子，削尖桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插村口，插屋旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋地下，做桩坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂空中，叫吊桩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖桩吓得敌人晕头转向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕刺透脑袋，戳穿肚肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到半死不活抬出陷阱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖桩还连在鬼子身上。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南南方遍地是尖桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个越南就是一根尖桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎进了约翰逊的嘴巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卡在他喉咙正中央。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咽不下，吐不出，痛得慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有一肚子花言巧语也唱不成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿尖桩能“无条件”给拔出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好让我这刽子手恢复健康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕掉进陷阱的美军被他们同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴拉出来抬走时，身上还"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着尖桩。事见《南方来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信》第二集。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}